@host = http://localhost:1323

### 健康检查 / 根路径
# GET {{host}}/

### 搜索接口：接收多值查询参数 tag
GET {{host}}/demo/search?tag=go&tag=web&tag=api

### 调试接口：接收路径参数 str
GET {{host}}/demo/err/debug/hello

### 测试接口：通过手机号查询用户（MySQL），不存在则自动创建
GET {{host}}/demo/user/phone

### SHA256 哈希计算：传入 text 参数返回 SHA256 哈希值
GET {{host}}/demo/sha256?text=hello

### SHA256 哈希计算：空字符串
GET {{host}}/demo/sha256?text=

### SHA256 哈希计算：中文文本
GET {{host}}/demo/sha256?text=%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD

### SHA256 哈希计算：缺失参数（应返回错误）
GET {{host}}/demo/sha256

### Common - 应用版本信息
GET {{host}}/common/version

### Common - 更新日志
GET {{host}}/common/changelog

### Common - 应用设置
GET {{host}}/common/setting

### CORS - OPTIONS Preflight (模拟浏览器预检请求)
OPTIONS {{host}}/demo/search
Origin: https://example.com
Access-Control-Request-Method: POST

### CORS - GET with Origin (模拟跨域 GET 请求)
GET {{host}}/demo/sha256?text=hello
Origin: https://example.com

### CORS - Same-Origin (无 Origin 头，同源请求)
GET {{host}}/demo/sha256?text=hello

### CORS - OPTIONS without Access-Control-Request-Method
OPTIONS {{host}}/demo/sha256
Origin: https://example.com

### MySQL CRUD - 创建用户
POST {{host}}/demo/usr
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "张三",
  "phone": "13800138000",
  "age": 25
}

### MySQL CRUD - 查询单个用户
GET {{host}}/demo/usr/1

### MySQL CRUD - 更新用户
PUT {{host}}/demo/usr/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "张三丰",
  "age": 30
}

### MySQL CRUD - 查询用户列表
GET {{host}}/demo/usrs

### MySQL CRUD - 删除用户
DELETE {{host}}/demo/usr/1
